        Parameters:
        browser - the browser instance on which the event is initially occurred. -最初发生事件的浏览器实例。
        level - the console message level (debug, log, warning or error). -控制台消息级别（调试，日志，警告或错误）。
        lineNumber - the line number that causes the message. -导致该消息的行号。
